comments.content: Could be wrong but looks hand-done to me. Reminds me a bit of [Delicious](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/yes-please/delicious-pro). Some more I like as alternative: MAWNS [Lakesight](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.aringtypeface.com/lakesight), [Stainy](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.aringtypeface.com/stainy), [Amplify](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.aringtypeface.com/amplify), [Mastoc](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.aringtypeface.com/mastoc) and [Intrique](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.aringtypeface.com/intrique-script), artimasa [Thander](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/creativemarket.com/artimasa/110776-Thander), [Felisha](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/creativemarket.com/artimasa/87026-Felisha), [Steady](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/creativemarket.com/artimasa/65815-Steady) and [Nabila](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/creativemarket.com/artimasa/60790-Nabila), [Parsley Script](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/bluevinyl/parsley-script), [Sauber Script](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/typejockeys/sauber-script), [Machiarge](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/flat-it/machiarge), [Nexa Rust Script R OO](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/font-fabric/nexa-rust/script-r-00), [Cider](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/suomi/cider), [Brand](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094718/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/argentina-lian-types/brand)
